Left arm.

201
00:14:30,720 --> 00:14:32,119
Legs.

202
00:14:34,120 --> 00:14:37,396
I can't move. I can't move.
What's going on?

203
00:14:37,520 --> 00:14:38,669
Get ice now.

204
00:14:38,760 --> 00:14:40,955
I can't breathe.
I can't breathe.

205
00:14:41,800 --> 00:14:43,995
